{"tid":1632481,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【和理非力量】我ig 瘋狂dm文宣比美國議員...","createTime":"2019-10-06T18:11:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T18:57:13.000Z","uid":48873,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7f35eb1be24f0e89b5ba4cc3cac8af00b5ca4147","tid":1632481,"uid":48873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:11:58.000Z","msg":"已經send到佢暫停咗我個dm功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啱先見到條非禮片，又再一次洗曬全部女權ig<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有係成效我未知，但起碼我見到有部分已讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知你有無嬲到想全世界睇到黑警暴行？<br />\n嬲到想即刻殺曬d黑警？<br />\n嬲到唔知點發洩？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎學習鍵盤戰士戰線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上台灣論壇<br />\n上twitter<br />\n上baby kingdom<br />\n上香討<br />\n上reddit <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下載文宣圖片 瘋狂傳發<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你接觸一個人 佢有可能再send出去<br />\n<br />\n唔洗文筆好， 只要加句「請轉發」 ，廣告心理學上叫call to action, 就有可能多個人幫你分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nIg既朋友 請hashTag: <br />\n#FightForFreedom<br />\n#StandWithHongKong<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑警咁鍾意玩呀嘛?<br />\nLet&rsquo;s battle with the world<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"5ff1ac8e0208a39afbb6a7c12740b544a0e85cb4","tid":1632481,"uid":48873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:12:55.000Z","msg":"認同請轉發<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我要全世界都睇到黑警暴行，唔好再掛住碌連登啦各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hk